{"tid":519954,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓成日痾係地下 點解決？","createTime":"2018-01-05T01:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T02:35:48.000Z","uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"06688e761a0a659303f9212f7556df300860fc7e","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"放咗個貓沙盤係果個位 佢都依然係附近痾尿<br />\n已經維持咗一段時間 好困擾 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c529b8e2ac0c5ec72cbbf3d29d0ed7150ab4a97","tid":519954,"uid":157433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"一見到佢想痾就捉佢入砂盤，跟住摸頭讚佢<br />\n一係捉佢入籠，砂盤放埋入去，每次用岩都讚佢，等佢知道咁樣做先岩<br />\n<br />\n利申：隻貓兩個月第一次入屋企已識用貓砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9153c4ed6b794643f8fdfc8ca8fcf59463d8e75","tid":519954,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"對待主子要耐心，耐心，再耐心。<br />\n<br />\n唔好用教人嘅方式對待主子，因為佢哋嘅智商唔會太高，佢哋唔識得將兩種事情嘅因果合埋一齊諗，所以要你呢個奴隸去一次又一次咁去重複，令佢習慣咗，當然佢都仲係唔會明嗰因果關係嘅，但佢知屙完就有嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d1fd5ef2507d254d37560996e11f977004f28b","tid":519954,"uid":122514,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T02:58:58.000Z","msg":"動物傳心術問下佢點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324d3be7dc7d30a98994eb9f86ac0919fd61c761","tid":519954,"uid":150485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物傳心術問下佢點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a52a2031b4104ebb3f4ebbee8161869b2f8ea2","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物傳心術問下佢點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係問點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bcf104882716cc098833e3391e3b2eb2e58265","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對待主子要耐心，耐心，再耐心。<br />\n<br />\n唔好用教人嘅方式對待主子，因為佢哋嘅智商唔會太高，佢哋唔識得將兩種事情嘅因果合埋一齊諗，所以要你呢個奴隸去一次又一次咁去重複，令佢習慣咗，當然佢都仲係唔會明嗰因果關係嘅，但佢知屙完就有嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 其實佢多數會入貓沙<br />\n但每朝一起身 就見佢痾咗係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740a163364eae648a4a47435ea0c519223e71954","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一見到佢想痾就捉佢入砂盤，跟住摸頭讚佢<br />\n一係捉佢入籠，砂盤放埋入去，每次用岩都讚佢，等佢知道咁樣做先岩<br />\n<br />\n利申：隻貓兩個月第一次入屋企已識用貓砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係我放緊教既時候痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb1f1a9ded6c5a4194dd249b4cc8ae7cbb16d6f","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一見到佢想痾就捉佢入砂盤，跟住摸頭讚佢<br />\n一係捉佢入籠，砂盤放埋入去，每次用岩都讚佢，等佢知道咁樣做先岩<br />\n<br />\n利申：隻貓兩個月第一次入屋企已識用貓砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係我訓緊教既時候痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"09fc2d274585494122d8cd608a58e9190e93fad7","tid":519954,"uid":162043,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"你只要將貓砂鋪滿全間屋 佢就冇辨法痾到係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa805f25270888af083fe7909dba160f6ac11109","tid":519954,"uid":123043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"個陣我家主子啱啱黎屋企, Farm Cat 黎, 所以佢集慣係一堆野到痾<br />\n棉被又痾過, 一堆衫入面又痾過<br />\n俾我發現左之後放個貓砂盤係佢面前, 抱佢入個盤到,<br />\n佢坐左陣  諗住行開個陣又抱番佢入去, loop十幾廿次<br />\n之後佢就識自己係個盤到痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d4120dc1de0f6d3cc4a47605a817880671e559","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣我家主子啱啱黎屋企, Farm Cat 黎, 所以佢集慣係一堆野到痾<br />\n棉被又痾過, 一堆衫入面又痾過<br />\n俾我發現左之後放個貓砂盤係佢面前, 抱佢入個盤到,<br />\n佢坐左陣  諗住行開個陣又抱番佢入去, loop十幾廿次<br />\n之後佢就識自己係個盤到痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我果隻其實本身都識用貓砂<br />\n係襯我地訓曬教就痾一篤係地下度 痾完仲要用手挖黎挖去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ae66f549309957c002f459b8ed773b79cdb082","tid":519954,"uid":142053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43d4120dc1de0f6d3cc4a47605a817880671e559","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣我家主子啱啱黎屋企, Farm Cat 黎, 所以佢集慣係一堆野到痾<br />\n棉被又痾過, 一堆衫入面又痾過<br />\n俾我發現左之後放個貓砂盤係佢面前, 抱佢入個盤到,<br />\n佢坐左陣  諗住行開個陣又抱番佢入去, loop十幾廿次<br />\n之後佢就識自己係個盤到痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我果隻其實本身都識用貓砂<br />\n係襯我地訓曬教就痾一篤係地下度 痾完仲要用手挖黎挖去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:30:19.000Z","msg":"痾完就挖係天性嚟既 如果佢喺你訓咗先咁做 可能係佢嫌個沙盤污糟 因為我屋企隻衰野就係咁 佢去完我未執 佢就嫌個沙盤污糟 然後週圍痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c733694e8a1ff54704f99b1efaaba9cb17952aa","tid":519954,"uid":146431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:08:57.000Z","msg":"你用咩貓沙先？<br />\n可能係太硬身佢踩落去唔舒服/佢唔中意<br />\n試下換第二隻貓沙睇下點"},{"pid":"47bf6829dd3c05971bde62518db7d462ab0f3763","tid":519954,"uid":130016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:21:32.000Z","msg":"可能佢唔鍾意用緊個款貓砂/貓砂盤/放既位置，要逐樣試睇下邊度出咗問題，希望下面條片幫到你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BzliLSt7myE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBzliLSt7myE&d=wxO4TvblOyXzBSP4btRs8%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5e70d6d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BzliLSt7myE</a>"},{"pid":"0a770fb41ff90f84ea86e63376010cce6bb4e50e","tid":519954,"uid":47681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"係咪你等佢痾好多篤先剷<br />\n<br />\n我有隻貓好衰<br />\n每次行入屎兜要痾番指定個一個位<br />\n個個位有野未清你就死硬 <br />\n因為佢會係你張床度痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecf35c90ee146a69fe6cddb389292c04ba725dc","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T23:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔該各位巴絲 我再試下轉貓砂<br />\n佢頭先入痾咗篤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852da30b56689d6e6d81414c83602f2d12280dd5","tid":519954,"uid":122514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5a52a2031b4104ebb3f4ebbee8161869b2f8ea2","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>動物傳心術問下佢點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係問點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"好啦講笑啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前主人都係咁 成日係貓屎盤前面解決都唔行多步入去<br />\n後來發現係貓砂唔夠多 佢發脾氣抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c3dde7e14a38f278d28008e88e877fb3725686","tid":519954,"uid":76463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"樓主貓貓d wewe 同💩💩正唔正常啊？因為我隻貓都試過咁，點知佢係肚痾唔想整污糟個貓砂盆所以係地下痾，同佢睇左醫生食左藥就無事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11027e7c018d2082c8f57a6239fa6facced3b259","tid":519954,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"未閹，射尿霸地盤，點教都會繼續射"},{"pid":"ad4910101ddddd41d8f8c90a2b8e6b4faa0b9ef6","tid":519954,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"係尿既地方放食物"},{"pid":"5975ff4b4094e547b04ab852beb5e19f7e85aebf","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未閹，射尿霸地盤，點教都會繼續射</blockquote><br />\n佢絕咗育架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9ff847a4fc549ae8e16d8daa2de98bdf259fb3","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主貓貓d wewe 同💩💩正唔正常啊？因為我隻貓都試過咁，點知佢係肚痾唔想整污糟個貓砂盆所以係地下痾，同佢睇左醫生食左藥就無事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f577991e65de6eefb37c7564c23294e77c8ffc7","tid":519954,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5975ff4b4094e547b04ab852beb5e19f7e85aebf","tid":519954,"uid":140431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未閹，射尿霸地盤，點教都會繼續射</blockquote><br />\n佢絕咗育架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:42:41.000Z","msg":"咁你隻貓有潔癖，要瘋狂清廁所了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd1047527fff387cbafb5f5f4510db59edf895f","tid":519954,"uid":33370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11027e7c018d2082c8f57a6239fa6facced3b259","tid":519954,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"未閹，射尿霸地盤，點教都會繼續射"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"天性黎<br />\n你唯有閹左佢試下<br />\n但佢射慣左可能閹完都繼續射，你要有心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}